title: The Essential Louis Comfort Tiffany (Art Ebook)
description:
The Essential Louis Comfort Tiffany (Essential Series)
Harry N. Abrams, Inc. | 2001 | ISBN: 0810958287 | English | 120 pages | PDF | 13.7 MB

Louis Comfort Tiffany moved among the elite of his time, yet he sought to share his beautiful creations with a worldwide audience, not just the wealthy few. This is one of a popular series that focuses on the lives of individual artists. It features the work of Louis Comfort Tiffany, famous for his stained glass, vases, jewellery and furniture
